{"tid":547750,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★[安樂死] 日本5ch討論區有自殺方法研究","createTime":"2018-02-01T18:31:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-10T05:33:44.000Z","uid":160807,"like":12,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"db9085b045afa46ec3aa6481efee267ffd8e6c18","tid":547750,"uid":160807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T18:31:27.000Z","msg":"香港根本須要安樂死合法化<br />\n但係政府一直冇重視安樂死訴求<br />\n日本人係呢方面既意識就先進過香港好多<br />\n5ch係一個同連登好相似既地方<br />\n一直都有d貼比大家傾下提供下好嘅自殺方法<br />\n目前已經開到第9個<br />\n<br />\n【首吊り・練炭】自殺方法研究スレ9【硫化水素・その他etc.】<br />\n<a href=\"https://itest.5ch.net/krsw/test/read.cgi/mental/1514810353\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fitest.5ch.net%2Fkrsw%2Ftest%2Fread.cgi%2Fmental%2F1514810353&d=8FR%2FH2FOr0q1scos%2BgoAVm6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=794c5074\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://itest.5ch.net/krsw/test/read.cgi/mental/1514810353</a>"},{"pid":"9daa77ad8e6e413f32a024a71f9d92af0691da3e","tid":547750,"uid":53794,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T18:32:31.000Z","msg":"2ch 5ch其實有咩分別"},{"pid":"0d2320e6cc6345ceceaddae7528f3fd0e0e1d93b","tid":547750,"uid":160807,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"9daa77ad8e6e413f32a024a71f9d92af0691da3e","tid":547750,"uid":53794,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T18:32:31.000Z","msg":"2ch 5ch其實有咩分別"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T18:35:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/2ch\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F2ch&d=8FR%2FH2FOr0q1scos%2BgoAVm6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=8ea4d7e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/2ch</a><br />\n2017年10月1日起更名為5ch"},{"pid":"4f358254c8d6a022126c9e98d12003aa18d10891","tid":547750,"uid":35716,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T18:36:23.000Z","msg":"以前本完全自殺手冊都係日本人寫...."},{"pid":"d39686a2a5b0606d1a2614c0acea43f7f1f7ac7a","tid":547750,"uid":160807,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T20:58:51.000Z","msg":"有冇連登仔識翻譯日文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff5166fbaf90457ddbdabb0e3e3bfb3eceb648f1","tid":547750,"uid":160807,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d39686a2a5b0606d1a2614c0acea43f7f1f7ac7a","tid":547750,"uid":160807,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T20:58:51.000Z","msg":"有冇連登仔識翻譯日文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T21:00:11.000Z","msg":"<del>酒と吊りの組み合わせなら成功率高い</del><br />\n酒和吊頸的組合成功率很高<br />\n<br />\n有冇譯錯? 用google翻譯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9360a5acb79161bb4b90eea4259149c62ca61f95","tid":547750,"uid":160807,"like":1,"dislike":18,"score":-17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T21:06:36.000Z","msg":"[url]凍死するならウォッカとか強い睡眠薬飲んで低体温症でそのまま寝れば死ねるだろうけど豪雪地帯の登れる山で人来ない所探さないといけないし方法的には非常に面倒だろうよ <br />\n<br />\n手足とか耳は千切れる位痛そうだし凍死選ぶ理由は分からん <br />\n<br />\n遺体が割と綺麗位しか無いやろ<br />\n[/url]<br />\n<br />\n如果你被凍死伏特加或強力的睡眠藥物如果你的睡眠是因為體溫過低，你會死亡，但你將不得不找到一個地方，人們不會進入這個高山雪地區可以爬上山這將是非常麻煩的方式<br />\n<br />\n四肢和耳朵似乎是痛苦的，因為它似乎打破了喉嚨，我不知道為什麼我選擇凍結和死亡<br />\n<br />\n屍體只有一個美麗的位置"},{"pid":"c195e6f97f9dfd9e63b2ff880c7b37ebe133cde8","tid":547750,"uid":160807,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T21:17:45.000Z","msg":"<del>二酸化炭素中毒で一気に死ねなかった場合、 <br />\n意識不明状態、あるいは意識はあるのにカラダが動かない状態などから酸欠で死ぬことになるだろうね <br />\nそうなれば苦しいから、保険として眠剤を使うわけでしょ</del><br />\n<br />\n如果不能立即死於二氧化碳中毒，<br />\n你可能會由於無意識狀態缺氧而死亡，或者是有意識的身體沒有移動的狀態<br />\n如果是這樣痛苦，你可以使用失眠作為安眠藥<br />\n<br />\ngoogle翻譯"},{"pid":"574a65472ecd90dc64d7570232345555a44757cc","tid":547750,"uid":72801,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T22:05:53.000Z","msg":"可惜睇唔明日文"},{"pid":"c7a9a663cab9ffeace429d2d5e0dc9a70a564ea1","tid":547750,"uid":54927,"like":2,"dislike":35,"score":-33,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T22:25:59.000Z","ms